document_data.History:
Essembra was settled when the Ordulin-Hillsfar road was cut through the Elven Court.{{cite book/Dragons of Faer√ªn|97}}

For centuries, Essembra was barely even a hamlet. When Aencar became the Warlord of Battledale in [[1030 DR]], he declared Essembra to be his seat since it was near his [[Aencar's Manor|ancestral manor]]. Aencar's chief lieutenant, [[Ramorth Wyvernblade]], took the title of lord of Essembra and built his manorhouse there.

In [[1422 DR]] [[Sembia]]ns allied with [[Netheril]] fought forces from [[Myth Drannor]] near Essembra.  The battle forced abandonment of the town.
